    "body": "### Description\n\n### Problem:\nThe current Angular LSP configuration in LazyVim only recognizes angular.json and nx.json as root patterns. However, Angular also uses project.json files, particularly in standalone components and libraries. This prevents the LSP from attaching to buffers in projects that use project.json.\n\n### Solution:\nThe Angular LSP should recognize `project.json` as a valid root pattern, allowing it to properly attach to buffers in all Angular project types.\n\n### Proposed Change:\n``` lua\n  recommended = function()\n    return LazyVim.extras.wants({\n      root = {\n        \"angular.json\",\n        \"nx.json\", \n        \"project.json\", -- support for standalone components and libraries\n      },\n    })\n  end,\n```",
